IN THE HIGH COURT OF RAJASTHAN AT JODHPUR
Arbitration Application No. ____ / 2026

M/s. Rajputana Infra Projects Pvt. Ltd.   ...Petitioner
Versus
National Highways Authority of India      ...Respondent

Application under Section 11(6) of the Arbitration and Conciliation Act, 1996 for appointment of Sole Arbitrator / Arbitral Tribunal.

May it please the Hon'ble Chief Justice,

1. The Petitioner invokes Clause 26 of the GCC for resolving disputes totaling ₹55.30 Crore arising out of NH-758 Contract.
2. The Respondent failed to act on the Petitioner's invocation notice dated 20.02.2026.
3. Therefore, an independent Arbitrator should be appointed.
